InflowDef.Name: kahua_Contract.ContractsIn
InflowDef.Description: Create and update expense contracts.  This provides for inflow of contract, contract item, and subsidiary contract items under contract items.  Statuses should be passed in with the status name string.  Workbreakdown items should be passed in as their codes.

TargetAttributes.Name: Status
TargetAttributes.Notes: Status string provided is resolved to matching contract status

TargetAttributes.Name: WorkBreakdownItem
TargetAttributes.Notes: Workbreakdown string provided is resolved to Kahua workbreakdown item reference
